---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Controllo - How to support Controllo"
  description="A short guide on how you can support Controllo."
  url="https://controllo.dlcastillop.com/how-to-support-controllo"
>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How to support Controllo</h1>
  <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-left">
    First of all we thank you for your interest in wanting to support Controllo.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-left">
    This project is free and open source. It is our desire to keep it that way
    and also make it viable and for that we need your help.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-left">You can support Controllo by:</p>
  <ul class="pt-6 text-lg text-left space-y-2">
    <li>
      ‚≠ê Leaving a star on the <a
        href="https://github.com/dlcastillop/controllo"
        class="link"
        target="_blank">GitHub repo</a
      >.
    </li>
    <li>
      üëç Rating the extension on the <a
        href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/controllo/bodddijlpmhpjplaajoigmejoglnjhif"
        class="link"
        target="_blank">Chrome Web Store</a
      >,
      <a
        href="https://addons.mozilla.org/es/firefox/addon/controllo/"
        class="link"
        target="_blank">Firefox Browser Add-Ons</a
      >
      and <a
        href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/controllo/hepodmbgelammobllblgaindjhahghgj"
        class="link"
        target="_blank">Edge Plugins</a
      >.
    </li>
    <li>ü§ù Sharing the extension with others.</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-left">Thank you!</p>
</BaseLayout>
